<h1>Order a box</h1>
<p>this should have the user select the right box and input all his information besides CC#</p>
<p>it should indicate delivery will occur starting next week, & all the detailed info they need to know before purchasing </p>
<p>We'll create a new Box object, which for convenience we'll include user data in as well.</p>
<p>Next page will confirm the transaction and ask them to enter CC info. </p>
<div class="row">

<%= form_for :box, url: boxs_path do |f| %>
  <fieldset>
    <legend>Choose your box</legend>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <ul class="inline-list">
          <li><%= radio_button_tag(:box_num, 1) %>
            <%= label_tag(:box_1, "Box 1") %></li>
          <li><%= radio_button_tag(:box_num, 2) %>
            <%= label_tag(:box_2, "Box 2") %></li>
          <li><%= radio_button_tag(:box_num, 3) %>
            <%= label_tag(:box_3, "Box 3") %></li>
          <li><%= radio_button_tag(:box_num, 4) %>
            <%= label_tag(:box_4, "Box 4") %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">

      <div class="large-4 columns">
            <%= f.text_field :firstname, :placeholder => "Your first name" %> 
      </div>
      <div class="large-4 columns">
            <%= f.text_field :lastname, :placeholder => "Last name"%>  
      </div>   
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>  
    </div>

    <div class="row">

      <div class="large-5 columns">
            <%= f.text_field :email, :placeholder => "Your email address" %> 
      </div>
      <div class="large-3 columns"><%= f.text_field :phone, :placeholder => "Your phone number" %> </div>  
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>  
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>  
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>  
    </div>
      
    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>  
      <div class="large-4 columns"></div>  
    </div>

    
          <%= f.submit 'Submit', :class => "button" %>
  </fieldset>     
<% end %>
